The paper discusses the challenges in ML-based security for SDN, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.LG) and the vulnerabilities in SDN (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper proposes the need for more secure developments in ML-based SDN security applications, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
